These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, baking
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Hobby   | baking  | collecting |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, house
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
2. the fan of house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | house |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, december
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| Birthday   | august | december |

 #################################

 
