.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, august
2 different pets are kept: cat, snake
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Birthday   | january | august |
| Pet           | snake     | cat  |

